Module org.nasdanika.html
Package org.nasdanika.html

Interface Input

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Consumer<Object>, Container<Input>, HTMLElement<Input>, InputBase<Input>, Markup, Producer
    public interface Input
extends InputBase<Input>, Container<Input>
    A generic UI element. It doesn't add any functionality, only binds UIElement and Container generic parameter to self for convenience.
    Author:
    Pavel
